        <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #f6861f;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">When you expand or collapse a snippet group from the Insert Snippet Link dialog, your setting carries over to the Insert Snippet drop-down in the local toolbar of the XML Editor, so you do not need to collapse the group in both locations. You can expand or collapse groups in the Insert Snippet drop-down at any time. </p>
